"""
╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  UNGPT v2.0 - Reasoning Handoff Architecture                                  ║
╠═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                                                                ║
║  FLOW WITH REASONING HANDOFF:                                                  ║
║  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  ║
║  │ Whisper Voice                                                            │  ║
║  │     ↓                                                                    │  ║
║  │ Gemini 3 Pro (browser/phone app)                                         │  ║
║  │   - Searches: pipeline, drive, memory, web                               │  ║
║  │   - Breaks into atomic chats                                             │  ║
║  │   - Writes tests for each                                                │  ║
║  │   - EXPLAINS REASONING → hands off to Perplexity                         │  ║
║  │     ↓                                                                    │  ║
║  │ Perplexity (local install + iPhone shortcut)                             │  ║
║  │   - Receives reasoning from Gemini                                       │  ║
║  │   - Researches all sources for context/upgrades                          │  ║
║  │   - Applies biz acumen                                                   │  ║
║  │   - EXPLAINS ALL PRIOR REASONING → hands off to SuperGrok                │  ║
║  │     ↓                                                                    │  ║
║  │ SuperGrok (iPhone shortcut)                                              │  ║
║  │   - Receives all prior reasoning                                         │  ║
║  │   - Searches X and Grokipedia                                            │  ║
║  │   - Applies biz acumen                                                   │  ║
║  │   - EXPLAINS REASONING → routes to Gemini Code Assist                    │  ║
║  │     ↓                                                                    │  ║
║  │ 10x Gemini Code Assist Standard (headless, common dashboard)             │  ║
║  │   - Receives full reasoning chain                                        │  ║
║  │   - Generates code                                                       │  ║
║  │   - Push to Git → PR → Merge → Cloud Run                                 │  ║
║  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  ║
║                                                                                ║
║  LLM-TO-LLM CONVERSATION: All LLMs can converse for clarification            ║
║  AUTORESEARCH_TRIAD: Full 650-agent complement on EACH LLM                    ║
║  STRUCTURE: Bottom-up CAV MTOE - squads research, leaders coalesce            ║
║                                                                                ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
"""

